cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with natural language processing and proposes a neural framework for semantic parsing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which makes cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) another likely category. The use of attention mechanisms suggests cs.LG (Learning), and the use of neural networks suggests cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves semantic relations and meaning representation, which suggests cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
